      "id": "PopularPost323102",
      "post_content": "This card is awesome. It's perfect for a [tibalt](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=tibalt) deck because it makes his random discard a lot less painful.  \n  \nI might try this in my [Tajic](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Tajic) EDH deck. I can reuse my [steelshaper's gift](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=steelshaper's gift) or one of my wrath cards (which there are a ton of). This would be a really good source of card advantage.  \n  \n6 mana to [wrath of god](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=wrath of god) again, and then 5 mana to s[teelshaper's gift](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=teelshaper's gift) again.",
      "posted_by": "SAUS3",
